<section class="gh-why">
  <div class="gh-why__inner">
    <div class="gh-section-header">
      <span class="gh-section-eyebrow gh-fade-up">Why Golden Herb Co.</span>
      <h2 class="gh-section-title gh-fade-up gh-stagger-1">Plant-Powered. Proven Results.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="gh-why__grid">
      <div class="gh-card gh-fade-up">
        <div class="gh-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 2C8 7 4 8 4 14a8 8 0 0016 0c0-6-4-7-8-12z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M12 14v4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="gh-card__title">Plant-Powered Formula</h3>
        <p class="gh-card__text">Every bar is crafted with turmeric root, kojic acid, and oat extract — ancient botanicals that have nourished skin for centuries. No filler. No compromise.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gh-card gh-fade-up gh-stagger-1">
        <div class="gh-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"/>
            <path d="M8 12l3 3 5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="gh-card__title">Visible Results</h3>
        <p class="gh-card__text">Most customers see brighter, more even skin within 2–3 weeks of daily use. Dark spots and hyperpigmentation visibly fade over time — naturally.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gh-card gh-fade-up gh-stagger-2">
        <div class="gh-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 21c-4.4 0-8-3.6-8-8 0-2.5 1.2-4.8 3-6.3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M12 21c4.4 0 8-3.6 8-8 0-2.5-1.2-4.8-3-6.3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="gh-card__title">Made for Everyone</h3>
        <p class="gh-card__text">Dry, oily, sensitive, or combination — our soap is formulated to work beautifully on all skin types. Unisex. Face and body. No exceptions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

